Package climate

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ClimateAverage
    This class essentially merges all the records with the same date by finding the mean of all the temperature means for each station in each date.
    ClimateCleanDatesAscending
    Climate cleaning for individual State files (or other).
    ClimateCleanStates
    This program will read in a large file containing many stations and states, and output in order the stations to their corresponding state file.
    ClimateDateComparator
    Simple helper class used for sorting the records by date.
    ClimateRecord
    This class holds a record of climate data.
    ClimateRecordList
    This class stores a list of all the climate records that share the same date.
